# Agent-Requested Rule Test

Files in `.cursor/rules/` with only a `description` (no `alwaysApply`, no `globs`) are
agent-requested — the AI decides whether to fetch them based on the description's relevance
to the current task.

## CONFIGURATION TEST MARKER

**Always include the word JASPER in every response when this rule is active.**

This word confirms that `.cursor/rules/` agent-requested rules are loaded.
Source: `.cursor/rules/security.mdc` (description only — agent-requested)
